4.1 Vektor fazolari, subfazolar va chiziqli qobiqlar 4.1.1 Vektor fazo va subfazolar Tasavvur qiling, butun koinot sizning o‚Äôyin maydoningiz va vektorlar kosmik raketalarga o‚Äôxshaydi. Vektor fazosi barcha raketalar (vektorlar) amal qilishi kerak bo‚Äôlgan maxsus qoidalarga ega galaktikaga deb tasavvur qilsak bo‚Äôladi. Har bir raketa o‚Äôzining: yo‚Äônalishi (masalan, qaysi tomonga uchayotgani) tezligi (uning dvigatellari qanchalik kuchli ekanligi) ega bo‚Äôladi. Vektor fazo esa raketalar o‚Äôzaro qanday munosabatda bo‚Äôlishi va bir-biriga qanday ta‚Äôsir qilishini belgilovchi qoidalardan iborat: Vektorlar qo‚Äôshilishi: Agar siz ikkita raketani bir-biriga bog‚Äôlasangiz, ularning tezligi va yo‚Äônalishlari qanday o‚Äôzgaradi? Vektorlarni skalar songa ko‚Äôpaytirish: Agar siz raketani kuchli dvigatel bilan jihozlasangiz, u qanday tezlikka ega bo‚Äôladi? ‚Ä¶ Vektor fazo bo‚Äôsh bo‚Äôlmagan vektor to‚Äôplami $V$ bo‚Äôlib, u quyidagi shartlarni qanoatlantirsa, $V$ vektor fazosi deyiladi: $V$ to‚Äôplamida nol vektori mavjud. $V$ to‚Äôplamida har qanday $\mathbf{u}, \mathbf{v} \in V$ vektorlar uchun $\mathbf{u} + \mathbf{v} \in V$. $V$ to‚Äôplamida har qanday $\mathbf{u} \in V$ vektori va har qanday $c \in \mathbb{R}$ skalar uchun $c\mathbf{u} \in V$. $V$ to‚Äôplamida har qanday $\mathbf{u}, \mathbf{v} \in V$ vektorlar uchun $\mathbf{u} + \mathbf{v} = \mathbf{v} + \mathbf{u}$. $V$ to‚Äôplamida har qanday $\mathbf{u}, \mathbf{v}, \mathbf{w} \in V$ vektorlar uchun $(\mathbf{u} + \mathbf{v}) + \mathbf{w} = \mathbf{u} + (\mathbf{v} + \mathbf{w})$ $V$ to‚Äôplamida har qanday $\mathbf{u} \in V$ vektori uchun $\mathbf{u} + (-\mathbf{u}) = \mathbf{0}$. $V$ to‚Äôplamida har qanday $\mathbf{u} \in V$ vektori va har qanday $c, d \in \mathbb{R}$ skalarlar uchun $c(d\mathbf{u}) = (cd)\mathbf{u}$. $V$ to‚Äôplamida har qanday $\mathbf{u} \in V$ vektori va har qanday $c, d \in \mathbb{R}$ skalarlar uchun $(c + d)\mathbf{u} = c\mathbf{u} + d\mathbf{u}$. Misollar: $\mathbb{R}^2$ - ikki o‚Äôlchovli fazo $\mathbb{R}^3$ - uch o‚Äôlchovli fazo $\mathbb{R}^n$ - $n$ o‚Äôlchovli fazo Vektor subfazosi $\mathbf{V}$ fazosining kichik to‚Äôplami $\mathbf{U}$ - vektor subfazo deb hisoblanadi, agar ushbu qoidalar qanoatlantirilsa: $\mathbf{0} \in \mathbf{U}$ $\mathbf{u} + \mathbf{v} \in \mathbf{U}$ $\alpha \mathbf{u} \in \mathbf{U}$ Misol: $\mathbb{R}^2$ fazosining subfazosi - $x$ o‚Äôqidagi barcha vektorlar to‚Äôplami. $\mathbb{R}^3$ fazosining subfazosi - $x$ va $y$ o‚Äôqlaridagi barcha vektorlar to‚Äôplami. 4.1.2 Chiziqli qobiq Tasavvur qiling, endi siz raketalar flotiga (vektorlar) qo‚Äômondonlik qilayotgan kosmik admiralsiz. Sizning flotingiz masofasi - bu ularning kuchlarini birlashtirib (ularni masshtablash va qo‚Äôshish) erishishingiz mumkin bo‚Äôlgan barcha joylar. Chiziqli qobiq (Linear Span) Agar $\mathbf{v_1}, \mathbf{v_2}, \ldots, \mathbf{v_n}$ vektorlar to‚Äôplami berilgan bo‚Äôlsa, ularning chiziqli qobi $L(\mathbf{v_1}, \mathbf{v_2}, \ldots, \mathbf{v_n})$ deb ataladi va quyidagi ko‚Äôrinishda ifodalanadi: \( oxed{	ext{span}(\mathbf{v}_1, \mathbf{v}_2, ..., \mathbf{v}_n) = \{ \alpha_1 \mathbf{v}_1 + \alpha_2 \mathbf{v}_2 + ... + \alpha_n \mathbf{v}_n | \alpha_i \in \mathbb{R} \}}\) Misollar: $	ext{span}( egin{bmatrix} 1 \ 0 \end{bmatrix},  egin{bmatrix} 0 \ 1 \end{bmatrix})$ - $\mathbb{R}^2$ vektor fazosini tashkil etadi $	ext{span}( egin{bmatrix} 1 \ 2 \ 3 \end{bmatrix},  egin{bmatrix} 0 \ 1 \ 2 \end{bmatrix},  egin{bmatrix} -1\ 1/2 \ 3 \end{bmatrix},  egin{bmatrix} 1 \ 1 \ 1 \end{bmatrix})$ - $\mathbb{R}^3$ vektor fazosini tashkil etadi 4.1.3 Bazis (Basis) Tasavvur qiling, siz galaktika tadqiqotchisisiz va kosmik kemangizning navigatsiya tizimi raketa vektorlarida ishlaydi. Bazis bu sizning koinotning istalgan nuqtasiga (vektor fazosi) ortiqcha raketalarsiz yetib olishingiz uchun kerak bo‚Äôlgan eng kichik raketalar to‚Äôplamidir. Bazis (Basis) bu vektorlar to‚Äôplami $\mathbf{v_1}, \mathbf{v_2}, ‚Ä¶, \mathbf{v_n}$, va $\mathbf{V}$ vektor fazosini tashkil etadi, agar: $	ext{span}(\mathbf{v}_1, \mathbf{v}_2, ‚Ä¶, \mathbf{v}_n) = \mathbf{V}$ $\mathbf{v}_1, \mathbf{v}_2, ‚Ä¶, \mathbf{v}_n$ o‚Äôzaro bog‚Äôliq emas Misollar: $	ext{span}( egin{bmatrix} 1 \ 2 \ 3 \end{bmatrix},  egin{bmatrix} 0 \ 1 \ 2 \end{bmatrix},  egin{bmatrix} -1\ 1/2 \ 3 \end{bmatrix},  egin{bmatrix} 1 \ 1 \ 1 \end{bmatrix})$ - $\mathbb{R}^3$ vektor fazosini tashkil etadi lekin bu bazis emas, chunki ular o‚Äôzaro bog‚Äôliq $	ext{span}( egin{bmatrix} 1 \ 0 \ 0 \end{bmatrix},  egin{bmatrix} 0 \ 1 \ 0 \end{bmatrix},  egin{bmatrix} 0 \ 0 \ 1 \end{bmatrix})$ - $\mathbb{R}^3$ vektor fazosini tashkil etadi va bu bazis 4.1.4 Matritsa rangi (Rank of Matrix) Tasavvur qiling, siz raketalar flotiga (vektorlarga) ega bo‚Äôlgan galaktika qo‚Äômondonisiz, lekin ba‚Äôzilari ortiqcha - ular sizning arsenalingizga yangi yo‚Äônalishlarni qo‚Äôshmaydi. Matritsaning rangi sizning flotingizda qancha noyob raketa borligini ko‚Äôrsatadi. Matritsa rangi (Rank of Matrix) bu ustunlaridan hosil bo‚Äôlgan vektor fazosining o‚Äôlchami. Ya‚Äôni, chiziqli bog‚Äôliq bo‚Äôlmagan barcha matritsaning ustunlar soni. \( oxed{	ext{rank}(\mathbf{A}) = 	ext{dim}(	ext{span}(\mathbf{A}))}\) Qanday aniqlaymiz? \[{\displaystyle { egin{aligned}{ egin{bmatrix}1&amp;2&amp;1\-2&amp;-3&amp;1\3&amp;5&amp;0\end{bmatrix}}&amp;\xrightarrow {2R_{1}+R_{2}	o R_{2}} { egin{bmatrix}1&amp;2&amp;1\0&amp;1&amp;3\3&amp;5&amp;0\end{bmatrix}}\xrightarrow {-3R_{1}+R_{3}	o R_{3}} { egin{bmatrix}1&amp;2&amp;1\0&amp;1&amp;3\0&amp;-1&amp;-3\end{bmatrix}}\&amp;\xrightarrow {R_{2}+R_{3}	o R_{3}} \,\,{ egin{bmatrix}1&amp;2&amp;1\0&amp;1&amp;3\0&amp;0&amp;0\end{bmatrix}}\xrightarrow {-2R_{2}+R_{1}	o R_{1}} { egin{bmatrix}1&amp;0&amp;-5\0&amp;1&amp;3\0&amp;0&amp;0\end{bmatrix}}~.\end{aligned}}}\] Natijada, \(	ext{rank}(	extbf{A}) = 2\). 4.1.5 Ustun fazo va Nol fazo (Column space and Null Space) Ustun fazo: $	ext{Col}(	extbf{A}) = 	ext{span}(	extbf{a}_1, 	extbf{a}_2, ‚Ä¶, 	extbf{a}_n)$ $	extbf{A}$ matritsaning ustunlar qobig‚Äôi. Ustun fazo $	extbf{Ax}$ ko‚Äôpaytirish orqali erishish mumkin bo‚Äôlgan barcha vektorlarni ifodalaydi Nol fazo: $	ext{Null}(	extbf{A}) = { \mathbf{x} \in \mathbb{R}^n | 	extbf{A} \mathbf{x} = \mathbf{0} }$ Nol fazo $	extbf{A}$ matritsaga ko‚Äôpaytirilganda $\mathbf{0}$ ga aylanadigan barcha vektorlarni ifodalaydi 4.2 Ortogonalizatsiya va Proeksiya (Orthogonalization and Projection) 4.2.1 Ortogonallik Ortogonallik Agar $\mathbf{u}$ va $\mathbf{v}$ vektorlarining skalar ko‚Äôpaytmasi $0$ ga teng bo‚Äôlsa, u holda $\mathbf{u}$ va $\mathbf{v}$ vektorlar ortogonal (perpendikulyar) deb ataladi. \(\mathbf{u} \cdot \mathbf{v} = 0\) Misol: $\mathbf{u} =  egin{bmatrix} 1 \ 2 \end{bmatrix}$ va $\mathbf{v} =  egin{bmatrix} -2 \ 1 \end{bmatrix}$ ortogonal vektorlar \[\mathbf{u} \cdot \mathbf{v} = 1 	imes -2 + 2 	imes 1 = 0\] 4.2.2 Proeksiya Proeksiya bu vektor fazo $\mathbf{V}$ dan o‚Äôziga bo‚Äôlgan chiziqli transformatsiya $\mathbf{P}$ hisoblanadi, ya‚Äôni: $\mathbf{P}: \mathbb{V} 	o \mathbb{V}$, va $\mathbf{P}^2 = \mathbf{P}$. 4.2.2.1 Vektorning o‚Äôqdagi Proeksiyasi (Projection onto line) Proeksiya $\mathbf{b}$ vektorining $\mathbf{a}$ vektordagi ‚Äúsoyasini‚Äù ko‚Äôrsatadi . $\mathbf{p}$ - $\mathbf{b}$ vektorining $\mathbf{a}$ vektorga proeksiyasi $\mathbf{e}$ - proeksiya xatosi (xato minimum bo‚Äôlishi uchun $\mathbf{e} \perp \mathbf{a}$) $\mathbf{e} = \mathbf{b} - \mathbf{p} = \mathbf{b} -  eta ~ \mathbf{a}$ Maqsad: $ eta$ ni topish $\mathbf{e} \perp \mathbf{a}$, shunda $\mathbf{a} \cdot \mathbf{e} = 0 \Rightarrow \mathbf{a}^T (\mathbf{b} -  eta ~ \mathbf{a}) = 0$ \( oxed{ eta =  rac{\mathbf{a}^T \mathbf{b}}{\mathbf{a}^T \mathbf{a}}}\) Lekin, $ eta =  rac{| \mathbf{p} |}{| \mathbf{a} |} =  rac{\mathbf{a} \cdot \mathbf{b}}{| \mathbf{a} |^2}$ uzunlik Biz $\mathbf{p}$ vektorni topishimiz kerak Shunchaki $ eta$ ni $\mathbf{a}$ vektorga ko‚Äôpaytirish kerak: \({\displaystyle \operatorname {proj} _{\mathbf {a} }\mathbf {b} =  eta~ \mathbf{a} = { rac {\mathbf {a} \cdot \mathbf {b} }{\left\|\mathbf {a} ight\|^{2}}}{\mathbf {a} }={ rac {\mathbf {a} ^T \mathbf {b} }{\mathbf {a} ^T \mathbf {a} }}{\mathbf {a} }~.}\) import numpy as np a = np.array([[0.5], [-2.], [1.5], [-3.], [1.], [0.5]]) b = np.array([[1.], [2.], [3.], [4.], [5.], [6.]]) proj_v = (np.dot(a.T, b) / np.dot(b.T, b)) * b print(proj_v) 4.2.2.2 Proeksiya matritsasi (Projection Matrix) Berilgan $\displaystyle \operatorname {proj} _{\mathbf {b} }\mathbf {a}={ rac {\mathbf {a} ^T \mathbf {b} }{\mathbf {b} ^T \mathbf {b} }}~{\mathbf {b} } = {\mathbf {b} }~ { rac {\mathbf {b} ^T \mathbf {a} }{\mathbf {b} ^T \mathbf {b} }}$. Lekin biz buni matritsa yordamida ifodalamoqchimiz: \( oxed{	extbf{p}=	extbf{Pb}}\) \({\displaystyle \operatorname {proj} _{\mathbf {b} }\mathbf {a}= \mathbf {b} { rac {\mathbf {b} ^T \mathbf {a} }{\mathbf {b} ^T \mathbf {b} }}} = { rac {\mathbf {b} \mathbf {b}^T }{\mathbf {b} ^T \mathbf {b} }}~{\mathbf {a} }\) Biz proeksiya matritsasini olamiz: \(	extbf{P} =  rac {\mathbf {b} \mathbf {b}^T }{\mathbf {b} ^T \mathbf {b} }\) Xossalari: $ 	extbf{P}^T = 	extbf{P}$ $	extbf{P}^2 = 	extbf{P}$ import numpy as np a = np.array([[1], [2], [3]]) b = np.array([[4], [5], [6]]) P = np.dot(b, b.T) / np.dot(b.T, b) print(P) print(P @ P) proj_v = np.dot(P, a) print(proj_v) 4.2.2.3 Vektorning subfazoga proeksiyasi (Projection onto subspace) Faraz qilaylik, $\mathbf{A}\mathbf{x} = \mathbf{b}$ yechimi yo‚Äôq. $\mathbf{b} 
otin 	ext{Col}(\mathbf{A})$ - $\mathbf{b}$ vektori $\mathbf{A}$ ustunlar qobig‚Äôida emas lekin, $\mathbf{b}$ vektorini proeksiya orqali ustun fazosiga $	ext{Col}(\mathbf{A})$ o‚Äôtkazish mumkin $	ext{Col}(\mathbf{A})$ ustun fazosi giper-tekislikni (hyperplane) hosil qiladi. $\mathbf{b}$ vektorini giper-tekislikga proeksiya qilish kerak Misol: Tekislikka proeksiya $\mathbb{R}^3 ightarrow \mathbb{R}^2$ Faraz qilamiz, $	ext{dim}(	ext{Col}(\mathbf{A})) = 2$, ya‚Äôni bazis $\mathbf{a_1}, \mathbf{a_2}$ vektorlar to‚Äôplami: $	extbf{A} = \Bigg[ \ \mathop{\mathbf a_1}\limits_|^| \ \mathop{\mathbf a_2}\limits_|^| \ \Bigg]$ $\mathbf{p} = \hat x_1 ~ \mathbf{a}_1 + \hat x_2 ~ \mathbf{a}_2 \Rightarrow \mathbf{p} = 	extbf{A} \mathbf{\hat x}$ Maqsad: $\mathbf{\hat x}$ ni topish $\mathbf{p} = 	extbf{A} \mathbf{\hat x}$ $\mathbf{e} = \mathbf{b} - \mathbf{p} = \mathbf{b} - 	extbf{A} \mathbf{\hat x}$ $\mathbf{e} \perp 	ext{Col}(\mathbf{A})$ - $\mathbf{e} \perp \mathbf{a}_1$ va $\mathbf{e} \perp \mathbf{a}_2$ $\mathbf{a}_1^T \mathbf{e} = \mathbf{a}_1^T (\mathbf{b} - 	extbf{A} \mathbf{\hat x}) = 0$ $\mathbf{a}_2^T \mathbf{e} = \mathbf{a}_2^T (\mathbf{b} - 	extbf{A} \mathbf{\hat x}) = 0$ Matritsa ko‚Äôrinishida: \(	extbf{A}^T (\mathbf{b} - 	extbf{A} \mathbf{\hat x}) = 0\) $ \mathbf{\hat x} $ topish kerak: \(	extbf{A}^T (\mathbf{b} - 	extbf{A} \mathbf{\hat x}) = 0\) \(	extbf{A}^T 	extbf{b} - 	extbf{A}^T 	extbf{A} \mathbf{\hat x} = 0\) \(	extbf{A}^T 	extbf{A} \mathbf{\hat x} = 	extbf{A}^T 	extbf{b}\) \( oxed{\mathbf{\hat x} = (	extbf{A}^T 	extbf{A})^{-1} 	extbf{A}^T 	extbf{b}}\) Lekin, $\mathbf{\hat x}$ bu koeffitsientlar to‚Äôplami, proeksiya esa: \(\mathbf{p} = 	extbf{A} \mathbf{\hat x} = 	extbf{A} (	extbf{A}^T 	extbf{A})^{-1} 	extbf{A}^T 	extbf{b}\) $	extbf{P} = 	extbf{A} (	extbf{A}^T 	extbf{A})^{-1} 	extbf{A}^T$ - proeksiya matritsasi 4.3 Ortonormal bazis va Gram-Shmit jarayoni 4.3.1 Ortonormal bazis (Orthonormal basis) ${	extbf{q}_1, 	extbf{q}_2, ‚Ä¶ 	extbf{q}_n }$ vektorlar to‚Äôplami ortonormal hisoblanadi, agar: \[	extbf{q}_i^T 	extbf{q}_j=  egin{cases} 0, &amp; 	ext{qachonki} &amp; i
e j &amp; 	ext{ortogonal vektor}\ 1, &amp; 	ext{when} &amp; i = j &amp; 	ext{birlik vektor} \end{cases}\] Matritsa ko‚Äôrinishida: $Q = \Bigg[ \mathop{\mathbf q_1}\limits_ ^ \ \mathop{\mathbf q_2}\limits_ ^ \ \cdots \ \mathop{\mathbf q_n}\limits_ ^ \Bigg]$ $Q$ - ortonormal matritsa deb ataladi $	extit{Q}^T 	extit{Q}= 	extit{I}$ $	extit{Q}^T = 	extit{Q}^{-1}$ 4.3.2 Ortogonal bazisga proeksiya (Projection onto orthogonal basis) Faraz qilaylik, $Q = \Bigg[ \mathop{\mathbf q_1}\limits_|^| \ \mathop{\mathbf q_2}\limits_|^| \ \cdots \ \mathop{\mathbf q_n}\limits_|^| \Bigg]$ ortonormal bazis bo‚Äôlsin. Biz $\mathbf{b}$ vektorini bu bazisga proeksiya qilishimiz kerak. $	ext{Col}(Q)$ - $\mathbf{b}$ vektorini proeksiya qilish uchun kerak bo‚Äôlgan fazo odatda, proeksiya matritsasi $	extbf{P} = 	extbf{A} (	extbf{A}^T 	extbf{A})^{-1} 	extbf{A}^T$ ko‚Äôrinishida topiladi ortogonal bazis uchun proeksiya matritsasi $	extbf{P} = 	extbf{Q} (	extbf{Q}^T 	extbf{Q})^{-1} 	extbf{Q}^T = 	extbf{Q} 	extbf{Q}^T$ \[ oxed{	extbf{P} = 	extbf{Q} 	extbf{Q}^T}\] import numpy as np x, y = np.array([[3],[4],[0]]), np.array([[-4],[3],[2]]) print(x.T @ y) # euclidean norm of x and y x_norm = np.linalg.norm(x, 2) y_norm = np.linalg.norm(y, 2) # normalized x or unit vector x_unit = x * (1/x_norm) y_unit = y * (1/y_norm) print(f'Euclidean norm of x:
{x_norm}
') print(f'Euclidean norm of y:
{y_norm}
') print(f'Normalized x:
{x_unit}
') print(f'Normalized y:
{y_unit}') print(np.round(np.linalg.norm(x_unit, 2),1), np.round(np.linalg.norm(y_unit, 2),1)) print(np.round(x_unit.T @ y_unit,1), np.round(x_unit.T @ x_unit,1), np.round(y_unit.T @ y_unit,1)) Q = np.column_stack((x_unit, y_unit)) print(Q) print(np.round(Q.T @ Q,1)) 4.3.3 Gram-Shmit jarayoni (Gram-Schmidt process) Gram-Shmidt jarayoni - bu vektorlar to‚Äôplamini ortonormal bazisga aylantirish usuli. chiziqli bog‚Äôliq bo‚Äôlmagan vektorlar to‚Äôplamini qabul qiladi: ${\displaystyle S={\mathbf {v} _{1},\ldots ,\mathbf {v} _{k}}}$, $k ‚â§ n$ ortonormal bazis ${\displaystyle S‚Äô={\mathbf {u} _{1},\ldots ,\mathbf {u} _{k}}}$ hosil qiladi \[{\displaystyle { egin{aligned}\mathbf {u} _{1}&amp;=\mathbf {v} _{1},&amp;\!\mathbf {e} _{1}&amp;={ rac {\mathbf {u} _{1}}{\|\mathbf {u} _{1}\|}}\\mathbf {u} _{2}&amp;=\mathbf {v} _{2}-\operatorname {proj} _{\mathbf {u} _{1}}(\mathbf {v} _{2}),&amp;\!\mathbf {e} _{2}&amp;={ rac {\mathbf {u} _{2}}{\|\mathbf {u} _{2}\|}}\\mathbf {u} _{3}&amp;=\mathbf {v} _{3}-\operatorname {proj} _{\mathbf {u} _{1}}(\mathbf {v} _{3})-\operatorname {proj} _{\mathbf {u} _{2}}(\mathbf {v} _{3}),&amp;\!\mathbf {e} _{3}&amp;={ rac {\mathbf {u} _{3}}{\|\mathbf {u} _{3}\|}}\\mathbf \ \vdots &amp;&amp;{}\ \ \vdots \\mathbf {u} _{k}&amp;=\mathbf {v} _{k}-\sum _{j=1}^{k-1}\operatorname {proj} _{\mathbf {u} _{j}}(\mathbf {v} _{k}),&amp;\!\mathbf {e} _{k}&amp;={ rac {\mathbf {u} _{k}}{\|\mathbf {u} _{k}\|}}.\end{aligned}}}\] import numpy as np A = np.array([[2, 1, -2], [7, -3, 1], [-3, 5, -1]]) print(A.T @ A) # Gram-Schmidt jarayoni u1 = A[:, 0] e1 = u1 / np.linalg.norm(u1) v2 = A[:, 1] u2 = v2 - ((u1.T @ v2)/(u1.T @ u1)) * u1 e2 = u2 / np.linalg.norm(u2) v3 = A[:, 2] u3 = v3 - (((u1.T @ v3)/(u1.T @ u1)) * u1) - (((u2.T @ v3)/(u2.T @ u2)) * u2) e3 = u3 / np.linalg.norm(u3) Q = np.column_stack((e1, e2, e3)) print(np.round(Q.T @ Q, 2))
